'''青蘋果書店'''（{{lang-en|'''Green Apple Books & Music'''}}）是一家位於[[美國|美國]][[舊金山|舊金山]]的[[獨立書店|獨立書店]]。1967年理查·薩伏依在克萊門街與第六街轉角的老房子創立了這家店。

青蘋果書店時常被{{le|舊金山灣區守衛者|San Francisco Bay Guardian}}<ref>{{Citation | title = 2006 Best Of The Bay: A Vision Of The Future | newspaper = San Francisco Bay Guardian | year = 2006 | url = http://www.sfbg.com/2006bob/readers.php | accessdate = 2015-01-06 | archive-date = 2006-08-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060813141304/http://www.sfbg.com/2006bob/readers.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>和{{le|舊金山週刊SF Weekly|}}<ref>{{Citation | title = Best Used Bookstores | newspaper = SF Weekly | date = 2005-05-11 | url = http://www.sfweekly.com/2005-05-11/best-of-san-francisco/best-used-bookstores/ | accessdate = 2015-01-06 | archive-date = 2011-06-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110610051836/http://www.sfweekly.com/2005-05-11/best-of-san-francisco/best-used-bookstores/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>的讀者選為最喜愛的二手書店和獨立書店。

